item.title: The Tunnel to Summer, the Exit of Goodbyes
item.description: Natsu e no Tonneru, Sayonara no Deguchi Original work written by Hachimoku Mei and illustrated by Kukka The movie was directed by Tomohisa Taguchi (Bleach: TYBW) Starring Ouji Suzuka as Touno Kaoru Iitoyo Marie as Hanashiro Anzu Hatanaka Tasuku as Kaga Shouhei Komiya Arisa as Kawasaki Koharu Terui Haruka as Hanamoto-sensei Koyama Rikiya as Touno's father Touno Karen as Touno Karen Produced by Ryoichiro Matsuo Just for some background, I was out of the country on a business trip and recently returned.
